Package srl.corpus

Interface Summary
Corpus.QueryHit Derive an object from this class to provide a callback on query success
Splitter This interface represents a sentence splitter and the functions it is supposed to provide
 

Class Summary
BeginTagToken Represents the opening tag of an entity
Corpus This class wraps Lucene to provide all the tools useful for access to the corpus.
EndTagToken Represents the closing tag of the entity
Processor Wraps the language processor, for easy interaction.
SrlDocument This object is used to represent a tokenized document or sentence.
SrlQuery This represents a query on the Corpus object.
SrlToken Identical to a Lucene token.
StandardSplitter Sentence splitter implementation.
